# Feature: Hooks in Cucumber Playwright Tests

#   Scenario: Using Before and After hooks
#     Given I have a Before hook that runs before each scenario
#     When I run a scenario
#     Then the Before hook should execute before the scenario steps

#   Scenario: Using BeforeAll and AfterAll hooks
#     Given I have a BeforeAll hook that runs once before all scenarios
#     And I have an AfterAll hook that runs once after all scenarios
#     When I run multiple scenarios
#     Then the BeforeAll hook should execute once before all scenarios
#     And the AfterAll hook should execute once after all scenarios
